            Have you ever wondered how well you're climbing, how much better
            you're getting after all these sessions you're putting in at the
            local climbing wall? Is all that effort you've put in at the gym
            actually paying off in terms of achieving the 7a route you've been
            wanting to crack? Are you training towards a competition? Or would
            you just like some objective feedback that your climbing is
            improving?
          </p>

