            How does The Internet work? When you type
            <code>www.google.com</code> into your browser bar and hit enter,
            what happens next? How does your instruction turn into a
            beautifully rendered page? What are all the moving parts that come
            into play to allow you &ndash; and, simultaneously, a billion other
            people &ndash; to surf the 'net?
          </p>

          <p>
            This is a quest to find out the answer. I already know lots of
            little bits of the puzzle, but there are some that I'm rusty about,
            or which have changed significantly in the past 20 years, so I've
            got plenty of research to do! Ultimately, I'm going to condense the
            results into a book but, in the meantime, I'm producing articles on
            various associated topics.
          </p>

